f18476e5397b707e392fbaee27a6035/09a33/walk-ons-check.png 1650w\" src=\"/static/2f18476e5397b707e392fbaee27a6035/06b13/walk-ons-check.png\" alt=\"Walk-On's Donation to UTSA Marching Band\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u>About The PM Group</u></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the San Antonio Business Journal. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, nonprofit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area nonprofit organizations in the last 15 years!  It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"Walk-On’s Donates $4,000 to UTSA Marching Band","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Walk-On&#8217;s Donates $4,000 to UTSA Marching Band","url":"/walk-ons-donates-4000-utsa-marching-band/"}],"title":"Walk-On's Bistreaux & Bar Supports UTSA Marching Band","metaDesc":"The UTSA Marching Band played for the attendees and Ron Ellis, UTSA Marching Band Director, received a $4,000 donation for their participation...","focuskw":"UTSA","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Walk-On's Bistreaux & Bar Supports UTSA Marching Band","opengraphDescription":"The UTSA Marching Band played for the attendees and Ron Ellis, UTSA Marching Band Director, received a $4,000 donation for their participation...","opengraphImage":{"altText":"UTSA Marching Band Performs at Walk-Ons VIP Event","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/upl